===Pronunciation===
גּלל / gâlal / gaw-lal' 

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''גּלל'''

# To [[roll]] (literally or figuratively): - commit, remove, roll (away, down, together), run down, seek occasion, trust, wallow.

